


				 l u c i l l e

			  Global Illumination Renderer


 features:
	- Monte Carlo ray tracing
	- Supports RIB( The RenderMan(R) Interface Bytestream ) file format
	- RenderMan Shading Language( limited and experimental )
	- Parallel Rendering( with MPI )
	- SIMD(x86 SSE) optimized ray tracing

 supported platform:
	- Mac OS-X
	- Linux( x86 )
	- Windows

 information:
        - home page
          http://lucille.sourceforge.net/

        - project management
          http://redmine.s21g.com/projects/show/lucille

 copyright:
	- 2003-2203 Syoyo FUJITA( syoyo@lucillerender.org )


 For more details on lucille, see doc direcotry and INSTALL file.






